name: E.I. Du Pont de Nemours & Company, Inc
title: Metals Industrial Corporation Customer feedback
description: It is refreshing to work with a company that has core values in line with Du Pont. I have never given a contractor this favorable a review. As a matter of fact, this may shock some folks! The project was truly Teamwork in Action – 17 million pounds of plant moved without an injury or argument – Wow! Your dedication and effort is appreciated.

name: Shell Chemical LP
title: Syndicate metals and alloys Customer feedback
description: I want to thank you and all the Syndicate metals and alloys team for the great job that you did for us on the VCM Area Civil/Structural Demolition Project. Your team worked safe, they worked well with all the other companies and personnel involved with the project, and they stuck to the original schedule. Again, thanks and I look forward to working with Syndicate metals and alloys again
